  "detailed_description": "<strong>WFO World Football Online</strong> is an online football management game with a non-scripted match engine on a virtual football world continuously developed by AI.<br><br>Footballers will grow up and retire in this time-free simulation.<br>In every occasion, you have a chance to drop cards to use them on your footballers to create super stars.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964760/extras/ff46cf59676682e40a1be065e38b41e4.poster.avif?t=1706701223\" width=206 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964760/extras/ff46cf59676682e40a1be065e38b41e4.webm?t=1706701223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964760/extras/ff46cf59676682e40a1be065e38b41e4.mp4?t=1706701223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964760/extras/3a39cc272dce618f3a98bb691e9c117f.poster.avif?t=1706701223\" width=206 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964760/extras/3a39cc272dce618f3a98bb691e9c117f.webm?t=1706701223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964760/extras/3a39cc272dce618f3a98bb691e9c117f.mp4?t=1706701223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique football world experience. WFO artificial intelligence generates the all of the footballers with their past and the future on the cloud server.<br></li><li>Non-scripted physic based realistic match engine.<br></li><li>AI generated scout system to generate footballers.<br></li><li>Live transfer market to buy/sell footballers.<br></li><li>Lighter management, more enjoyment.<br></li><li>Lots of in-game cards to develop your footballers.<br></li><li>Cross play support on the available platforms by linking your Steam account.</li></ul><br><i>Requires internet connection to play.<br>We don't collect any data from players.</i>",
